      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey ugh, my chest feels super tight and kinda like its burning right now. i had a massive burger and fries for dinner so i think it might just be really bad heartburn. my left arm feels a bit weird too, kinda tingly. should i just take some Tums and wait it out or is that a bad idea?",
